| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-2561 — Recovery Inhibition (dragonforce)"
| comment "Status: stable | Level: high | ID: 913679bd-b1a4-5c27-8d36-b9fd4f69352a"
